summary: A U.S. Customs and Border Protection TECS Person Encounter List generated by Kimberly Meder, detailing international flight travel records for two individuals (document numbers 526476667 and 094332776) between 2004 and 2019. keyFacts: The document is a law enforcement travel record (TECS Person Encounter List) generated by CBP Officer Kimberly Meder on April 6, 2021.
It tracks the international flight history of two individuals identified by document numbers 526476667 and 094332776 from 2004 to 2019.
The primary travel pattern shown is frequent flights between Los Angeles (LAX) and London (LHR), with Virgin Atlantic being a common carrier.
Other travel destinations include Miami, Vancouver, Manila, Nassau (Bahamas), Mexico City, and New York.
The document does not contain the actual names of the travelers, only their document numbers and travel details, indicating it is a redacted or summarized view for law enforcement purposes.
